nasm -f elf hello.S(asm) -o hello.o
The output is elf formt output file
sections and entry point

C calls functions in ASM file
functions need to declared as global in ASM
functions need a declaration in C

ASM calls functions in C
function need an extern func_name in ASM
call func_name in ASM

ELF = Executable and Linkable Format
ELF header + Program header table + Sections + section header table
